snippet.title: Mud Warriors [ Game Boy ] homebrew adventure game compatible to Nintendo Gameboy
snippet.description:
Hi guys,
Look! what I´ve found in the mud. 
It´s Ryan Veeder´s Mud Warriors compatible to Nintendo Game Boy.
This is really an adventure gem I digged out here, everyone has to play. 
It´s full of loveley deatils, an nostalgic story, great sound and graphics. This is everything a good Gameboy game needs. 

A Big shout out to Ryan Veeder and his Team, awsome work.
Took me back to my own childhood where I used to play in the mud and dirt. The days before kids had mobiles.

More informations here:
https://polyducks.itch.io/mud-warriors-gameboy

Credits:
Original Story/Characters by Ryan Veeder
Written by Ryan Veeder and Lance Campbell
Art and Creative Consulting by Polyducks
Programmed by Lance Campbell
Music by Ryan Veeder
Produced by Lance Campbell
